I tested this by require()ing a module called "module" that conflicts with our internal module.js:

app.js:
{code}
var module = require("module");
// Should be true
Ti.API.debug("isMyModule = " + module.isMyModule);
{code}

module.js:
{code}
exports.isMyModule = true;
{code}

Before the fix, this would fail. Now it works.
